org.eclipse.papyrus.designer.languages.common.profile.Codegen

Interface MavenProject

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Project
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MavenProjectImpl

    public interface MavenProject
extends Project
    A representation of the model object 'Maven Project'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Group Id
    • Artifact Id
    • Version
    • Arche Type
    • Dependencies
    • Parent
    • Properties
    • Base Package
    See Also:
    CodegenPackage.getMavenProject()
